..// settings.py
this is the heart of d project 
everything imp is stored here:
installed apps , database settings , templates settings , staic files middleware , secret key , debug key , allowed hosts without settings.py project will not run

..// urls.py :- this is the route manager.
it decides which url should go to which view ?

..// wsgi.py :- used when deploying ur django proj on a server (apache,nginx , etc.)

django app run avvadani ki server ki needed file

// asgi.py :- used for asynchronous applications
fastAPi style features :
.websockets
.chat apps 
.realtime notifications
File	             Use	                          Meaning
manage.py	       commands	                         Main control
init.py	           Makes folder a package	         Technical setup
settings.py	      All project settings	                Heart
urls.py	            URL routing                        	Map
wsgi.py	         Deploy on server	                  Production gateway
asgi.py	          Async support	                      Realtime gateway

